### PROGRAM IS FIGHTING GAME
## Turn-based fighting game
## Player and monter inheritanced from class Animal, having 4 status level, power, hp, mp
## Player have 2 more status is name and job
## monter have 2 type is pig and bird
## Starting program, name player was inputed from key board
## Status of player and monter, first turn be random
## Players will enter skills from the keyboard, 1 is normal attack, 2 is ultimate. The monster's skill will be random
## If use ultimate skill and mp lower mp need, the system will use normal skills instead
## The program ends when 1 of the 2 runs out of HP